[package]
name = "deltachat"
version = "1.159.3"
edition = "2021"
license = "MPL-2.0"
rust-version = "1.82"
repository = "https://github.com/chatmail/core"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
async-broadcast = "0.7.2"
async-channel = "2.3.1"
base64 = "0.22"
bytes = "1"
data-encoding = "2.7.0"
escaper = "0.1"
fast-socks5 = "0.10"
fd-lock = "4"
futures-lite = "2.6.0"
futures = "0.3.31"
hex = "0.4.0"
hickory-resolver = "=0.25.0-alpha.5"
http-body-util = "0.1.3"
humansize = "2"
hyper = "1"
hyper-util = "0.1.11"
kamadak-exif = "0.6.1"
libc = "0.2"
mailparse = "0.16.1"
mime = "0.3.17"
num_cpus = "1.16"
num-derive = "0.4"
num-traits = "0.2"
parking_lot = "0.12"
percent-encoding = "2.3"
pin-project = "1"
qrcodegen = "1.7.0"
quick-xml = "0.37"
quoted_printable = "0.5"
rand = "0.8"
regex = "1.10"
rust-hsluv = "0.1"
rustls-pki-types = "1.11.0"
sanitize-filename = "0.5"
serde_json = "1"
serde_urlencoded = "0.7.1"
sha-1 = "0.10"
sha2 = "0.10"
smallvec = "1.14.0"
strum = "0.27"
strum_macros = "0.27"
tagger = "4.3.4"
textwrap = "0.16.2"
thiserror = "2"
tokio-io-timeout = "1.2.0"
tokio-util = "0.7.14"
toml = "0.8"
url = "2"
webpki-roots = "0.26.8"
blake3 = "1.8.0"

[dev-dependencies]
futures-lite = "2.6.0"
log = "0.4"
nu-ansi-term = "0.46"
pretty_assertions = "1.4.1"
tempfile = "3.19.1"
testdir = "0.9.3"

[workspace]
members = [ "deltachat-ffi", "deltachat_derive", "deltachat-jsonrpc", "deltachat-rpc-server", "deltachat-ratelimit", "deltachat-repl", "deltachat-time", "format-flowed", "deltachat-contact-tools", "fuzz",]

[features]
default = [ "vendored",]
internals = []
vendored = [ "rusqlite/bundled-sqlcipher-vendored-openssl",]

[profile.dev]
debug = 0
panic = "abort"
opt-level = 1

[profile.test]
debug = 1
opt-level = 0

[profile.release]
lto = true
panic = "abort"
opt-level = "z"
codegen-units = 1
strip = true

[dependencies.deltachat_derive]
path = "./deltachat_derive"

[dependencies.deltachat-time]
path = "./deltachat-time"

[dependencies.deltachat-contact-tools]
path = "deltachat-contact-tools"

[dependencies.format-flowed]
path = "./format-flowed"

[dependencies.ratelimit]
path = "./deltachat-ratelimit"

[dependencies.async-imap]
version = "0.10.4"
default-features = false
features = [ "runtime-tokio", "compress",]

[dependencies.async-native-tls]
version = "0.5"
default-features = false
features = [ "runtime-tokio",]

[dependencies.async-smtp]
version = "0.10"
default-features = false
features = [ "runtime-tokio",]

[dependencies.async_zip]
version = "0.0.17"
default-features = false
features = [ "deflate", "tokio-fs",]

[dependencies.brotli]
version = "7"
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]

[dependencies.chrono]
features = [ "alloc", "clock", "std",]
version = "0.4.40"
default-features = false

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.25.6"
default-features = false
features = [ "gif", "jpeg", "ico", "png", "pnm", "webp", "bmp",]

[dependencies.iroh-gossip]
version = "0.33"
default-features = false
features = [ "net",]

[dependencies.iroh]
version = "0.33"
default-features = false

[dependencies.mail-builder]
version = "0.4.2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.pgp]
version = "0.15.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.rusqlite]
features = [ "sqlcipher",]
version = "0.32"

[dependencies.rustls]
version = "0.23.22"
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
features = [ "derive",]
version = "1.0"

[dependencies.shadowsocks]
version = "1.22.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "aead-cipher", "aead-cipher-2022",]

[dependencies.tokio-rustls]
version = "0.26.2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.tokio-stream]
version = "0.1.17"
features = [ "fs",]

[dependencies.tokio-tar]
version = "0.3"

[dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "fs", "rt-multi-thread", "macros",]
version = "1"

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1"
features = [ "serde", "v4",]

[dev-dependencies.anyhow]
features = [ "backtrace",]
version = "1"

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.5.1"
features = [ "async_tokio",]

[dev-dependencies.proptest]
version = "1"
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "rt-multi-thread", "macros",]
version = "1"

[workspace.dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
async-channel = "2.3.1"
base64 = "0.22"
futures = "0.3.31"
futures-lite = "2.6.0"
libc = "0.2"
log = "0.4"
mailparse = "0.16.1"
nu-ansi-term = "0.46"
num-traits = "0.2"
rand = "0.8"
regex = "1.10"
rusqlite = "0.32"
sanitize-filename = "0.5"
serde = "1.0"
serde_json = "1"
tempfile = "3.19.1"
thiserror = "2"
tokio = "1"
tokio-util = "0.7.14"
tracing-subscriber = "0.3"
yerpc = "0.6.4"

[workspace.dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.40"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.deltachat-contact-tools]
path = "deltachat-contact-tools"

[workspace.dependencies.deltachat-jsonrpc]
path = "deltachat-jsonrpc"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.deltachat]
path = "."
default-features = false

[lints.rust.unexpected_cfgs]
level = "warn"
check-cfg = [ "cfg(fuzzing)",]

[profile.dev.package."*"]
opt-level = "z"

[package]
name = "deltachat-contact-tools"
version = "0.0.0"
edition = "2021"
description = "Contact-related tools, like parsing vcards and sanitizing name and address. Meant for internal use in the deltachat crate."
license = "MPL-2.0"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
regex = "1.10"
rusqlite = "0.32"

[dependencies.chrono]
features = [ "alloc", "clock", "std",]
version = "0.4.40"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.anyhow]
features = [ "backtrace",]
version = "1"

[package]
name = "deltachat-jsonrpc"
version = "1.159.3"
description = "DeltaChat JSON-RPC API"
edition = "2021"
license = "MPL-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/chatmail/core"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
num-traits = "0.2"
schemars = "0.8.22"
async-channel = "2.3.1"
serde_json = "1"
tokio = "1"
sanitize-filename = "0.5"
walkdir = "2.5.0"
base64 = "0.22"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.19.1"
futures = "0.3.31"

[features]
default = [ "vendored",]
vendored = [ "deltachat/vendored",]

[dependencies.deltachat]
path = "."
default-features = false

[dependencies.deltachat-contact-tools]
path = "deltachat-contact-tools"

[dependencies.serde]
features = [ "derive",]
version = "1.0"

[dependencies.yerpc]
features = [ "anyhow_expose", "openrpc",]
version = "0.6.4"

[dependencies.typescript-type-def]
version = "0.5.13"
features = [ "json_value",]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "full", "rt-multi-thread",]
version = "1"

[package]
name = "deltachat-time"
version = "1.0.0"
description = "Time-related tools"
edition = "2021"
license = "MPL-2.0"

[dependencies]

[package]
name = "deltachat_derive"
version = "2.0.0"
edition = "2018"
license = "MPL-2.0"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
syn = "2"
quote = "1"

[package]
name = "format-flowed"
version = "1.0.0"
description = "format=flowed support"
edition = "2021"
license = "MPL-2.0"
keywords = [ "email",]
categories = [ "email",]

[dependencies]

[package]
name = "ratelimit"
version = "1.0.0"
description = "Token bucket implementation"
edition = "2021"
license = "MPL-2.0"

[dependencies]

[package]
name = "tao"
version = "0.33.0"
description = "Cross-platform window manager library."
authors = [ "Tauri Programme within The Commons Conservancy", "The winit contributors",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.74"
keywords = [ "windowing",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tauri-apps/tao"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/tao"
categories = [ "gui",]

[features]
default = [ "rwh_06", "x11",]
serde = [ "dep:serde", "dpi/serde",]
rwh_04 = [ "dep:rwh_04",]
rwh_05 = [ "dep:rwh_05",]
rwh_06 = [ "dep:rwh_06",]
x11 = [ "dep:gdkx11-sys", "dep:x11-dl",]

[workspace]
members = [ "tao-macros",]

[dependencies]
lazy_static = "1"
libc = "0.2"
log = "0.4"
bitflags = "2"
crossbeam-channel = "0.5"
url = "2"
dpi = "0.1"

[dev-dependencies]
image = "0.25"
env_logger = "0.11"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
optional = true
features = [ "serde_derive",]

[dependencies.rwh_04]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.rwh_05]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.5"
features = [ "std",]
optional = true

[dependencies.rwh_06]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.6"
features = [ "std",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"windows\\\")".dev-dependencies]
softbuffer = "0.4"

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"windows\\\")".dependencies]
parking_lot = "0.12"
unicode-segmentation = "1.11"
windows-version = "0.1"
windows-core = "0.61"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \\\"android\\\", target_os = \\\"windows\\\"))".dependencies]
once_cell = "1"

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"android\\\")".dependencies]
jni = "0.21"
ndk = "0.9"
ndk-sys = "0.6"
ndk-context = "0.1"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \\\"ios\\\", target_os = \\\"macos\\\"))".dependencies]
objc2 = "0.6"
block2 = "0.6"

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"macos\\\")".dependencies]
core-foundation = "0.10"
core-graphics = "0.24"
dispatch = "0.2"
scopeguard = "1.2"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \\\"linux\\\", target_os = \\\"dragonfly\\\", target_os = \\\"freebsd\\\", target_os = \\\"openbsd\\\", target_os = \\\"netbsd\\\"))".dependencies]
gtk = "0.18"
gdkwayland-sys = "0.18.0"
parking_lot = "0.12"
dlopen2 = "0.7.0"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "rwh_04", "rwh_05", "rwh_06", "serde", "x11",]
default-target = "x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu"
targets = [ "i686-pc-windows-msvc", "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc", "i686-unknown-linux-gnu", "x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu", "x86_64-apple-darwin",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"windows\\\")".dependencies.windows]
version = "0.61"
features = [ "Win32_Devices_HumanInterfaceDevice", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Globalization", "Win32_Graphics_Dwm", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi", "Win32_System_Com", "Win32_System_Com_StructuredStorage", "Win32_System_DataExchange", "Win32_System_Diagnostics_Debug", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_System_Memory", "Win32_System_Ole", "Win32_System_SystemServices", "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_System_WindowsProgramming", "Win32_System_SystemInformation", "Win32_UI_Accessibility", "Win32_UI_Controls", "Win32_UI_HiDpi", "Win32_UI_Input_Ime", "Win32_UI_Input_KeyboardAndMouse", "Win32_UI_Input_Pointer", "Win32_UI_Input_Touch", "Win32_UI_Shell", "Win32_UI_TextServices", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"android\\\")".dependencies.tao-macros]
version = "0.1.0"
path = "./tao-macros"

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"macos\\\")".dependencies.objc2-foundation]
version = "0.3"
default-features = false
features = [ "std", "NSArray", "NSAttributedString", "NSAutoreleasePool", "NSDate", "NSDictionary", "NSEnumerator", "NSGeometry", "NSObjCRuntime", "NSRange", "NSString", "NSThread", "NSURL",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"macos\\\")".dependencies.objc2-app-kit]
version = "0.3"
default-features = false
features = [ "std", "objc2-core-foundation", "NSApplication", "NSButton", "NSColor", "NSControl", "NSEvent", "NSGraphics", "NSImage", "NSOpenGLView", "NSPasteboard", "NSResponder", "NSRunningApplication", "NSScreen", "NSView", "NSWindow", "NSUserActivity",]

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \\\"linux\\\", target_os = \\\"dragonfly\\\", target_os = \\\"freebsd\\\", target_os = \\\"openbsd\\\", target_os = \\\"netbsd\\\"))".dependencies.gdkx11-sys]
version = "0.18"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \\\"linux\\\", target_os = \\\"dragonfly\\\", target_os = \\\"freebsd\\\", target_os = \\\"openbsd\\\", target_os = \\\"netbsd\\\"))".dependencies.x11-dl]
version = "2.21"
optional = true

[package]
name = "tao-macros"
description = "Proc macros for tao"
version = "0.1.3"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Tauri Programme within The Commons Conservancy",]
rust-version = "1.74"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
readme = "../README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tauri-apps/tao"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/tao-macros"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[features]
default = []

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1"
quote = "1"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2"
features = [ "full",]

[package]
name = "tauri-plugin-single-instance"
version = "2.2.3"
description = "Ensure a single instance of your tauri app is running."
authors = [ "Tauri Programme within The Commons Conservancy",]
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.77.2"
repository = "https://github.com/tauri-apps/plugins-workspace"
exclude = [ "/examples",]

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1"
tracing = "0.1"
thiserror = "2"

[features]
semver = [ "dep:semver",]
deep-link = [ "dep:tauri-plugin-deep-link",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.tauri]
version = "2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.tauri-plugin-deep-link]
path = "../deep-link"
version = "2.2.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.semver]
version = "1"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"linux\\\")".dependencies]
zbus = "5"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \\\"windows\\\")".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.59"
features = [ "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_System_DataExchange", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging", "Win32_Security", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi",]

[package.metadata.platforms.support.windows]
level = "full"
notes = ""

[package.metadata.platforms.support.linux]
level = "full"
notes = ""

[package.metadata.platforms.support.macos]
level = "full"
notes = ""

[package.metadata.platforms.support.android]
level = "none"
notes = ""

[package.metadata.platforms.support.ios]
level = "none"
notes = ""

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/chatmail/core"]
git = "https://github.com/chatmail/core"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
tag = "v1.159.3"

[source."https://github.com/simon-laux/tao"]
git = "https://github.com/simon-laux/tao"

branch = "hunt-down-open-url-crash-and-add-application_continue_user_activity"

[source."https://github.com/simon-laux/plugins-workspace"]

replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "simon/fix-macos-cwd-single-instance"
